For each of these evaluation criteria, a score in the interval [0,1] is typically obtained. Then, all the scores for a given ontology are aggregated into a composite relevance score, also in the interval [0,1]. This score represents the appropriateness of that ontology to describe the input data. The individual scores are combined in accordance with the following expression:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
